{"tid":2039422,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【2016旺角】暴動罪成囚七年 盧建民向終審法院提定罪上訴","createTime":"2020-05-28T04:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T17:06:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2277757466d387581dd7647d358d95b95d3baef9","tid":2039422,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:15:21.000Z","msg":"本土民主前線前發言人梁天琦、盧建民及黃家駒三人被指在2016年農曆年初二凌晨參與旺角騷亂，梁因襲警罪及暴動罪成被判囚六年，盧及黃則因暴動罪成分別被判囚七年及三年半。三人早前向高等法院申請上訴被拒，盧建民的代表律師表示已向上訴庭申請盧的定罪及判刑的上訴許可，亦已向終審法院申請定罪上訴，但只會以書面形式處理，不會開庭處理。<br />\n<br />\nsource: 頭條日報"},{"pid":"a4a4bb49defe9cdcc38925a4afbd0fcfa6f3f87a","tid":2039422,"uid":84409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b0bb56b0704122b9f78afe52bcce28f72feda1","tid":2039422,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4a4bb49defe9cdcc38925a4afbd0fcfa6f3f87a","tid":2039422,"uid":84409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"364b05003500ac7b01fc43483977b7141316a6d6","tid":2039422,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T05:01:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02dde730a5db3d5761873e502ddbb590ea1a54de","tid":2039422,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"364b05003500ac7b01fc43483977b7141316a6d6","tid":2039422,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T05:01:50.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,